rival - For the courier service option, the device will be delivered one business day before departure and will be collected one business day after arrival between 9:00am-5:30pm - For earlier collection, extra daily rental fees will be incurred - A penalty will be charged for late return at SGD 20 per day - Customer will be liable for any damage/lost/theft of device *Estimated Value of Products without Insurance* - WiFi device & SIM: SGD 300 - Carrying case: SGD 500 - Converter plug: SGD 50 - Acessories: SGD 25 - Power bank: SGD 50 - User guide: SGD 5 *Estimated Value of Products with Insurance* - WiFi device & SIM: SGD 100 - Carrying case: None - Converter plug: SGD 20 - Acessories: None - Power bank: SGD 20 - User guide: None *International Fair Usage Policy* - Under the Fair Usage Policy, users who deal with large amounts of data in a short period of time might, without prior notice, have their data usage limited at the discretion of the telecommunications company they are subscribed to - Please refrain from watching videos for a long time, or from using a huge amount of data in a short period of time - Yourwifi will in no way be responsible or liable for the incurred data limit as per above, and you will still be charged with the appropriate fees during your rental period","title":"3.5G WiFi (SG Pick Up) for Indonesia","ticketTypesAndPackages":[{"id":3312,"hasSeries":false,"name":"WiFi Device","currency":"SGD","favorited":false,"price":1.24,"variation":{"enumType":"gt.enumeration.Variation","name":"ADULT"},"issuanceLimit":null,"originalPrice":7.0,"settlementPrice":7.0,"merchantCurrency":"HKD","sourceName":"KLOOK UAT","sourceTitle":"Merchant","ableToDistributeToGlobaltix":false,"from":null,"did":3340965},{"id":3313,"hasSeries":false,"name":"WiFi Device + Power Bank","currency":"SGD","favorited":false,"price":1.59,"variation":{"enumType":"gt.enumeration.Variation","name":"ADULT"},"issuanceLimit":null,"originalPrice":9.0,"settlementPrice":9.0,"merchantCurrency":"HK